An Online Notice Board is a web-based application designed to display and manage important notices digitally, enabling fast and organized communication within an institution.

ğŸ” Admin Features
Secure admin login for authorized access.
Add new notices with title, content, and date.
Edit or update existing notices easily.
Delete outdated or incorrect notices.
Manage and monitor all notices from a centralized dashboard.

ğŸ“ Student Features
View all published notices in real time.
Access notices anytime through a user-friendly interface.
Read notices categorized by date or importance.
No login required for viewing notices (optional).
Stay updated with latest announcements efficiently.

Technologies Used:
HTML, CSS, PHP, MySQL, XAMPP, and Visual Studio Code.
